      "content": "A set of sensitive database credentials has been discovered in a publicly accessible GitHub repository. The exposed credentials include a username and password for a database named \"\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\" along with a private key. The credentials are stored in plaintext within a configuration file, making them directly accessible to anyone who can view the repository. This exposure represents a significant security risk as it violates the principle of secure credential management.",
